title: Browns beat Jets but don't impress, Steelers trade for Minkah Fitzpatrick (Football 9/17)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap the Browns 23-3 victory over the Jets on Monday Night Football (1:00). The guys unpack the unimpressive nature of Cleveland's win, New York's woes after losing another quarterback (9:00) and VisorGate brought to you by Odell Beckham Jr (23:00). The guys then react to the Dolphins trading Minkah Fitzpatrick to the Steelers for a 1st-round pick (28:00), Jalen Ramsey's trade request (41:00), and the future for Eli Manning as the Giants starter (52:00).
